item.title: C Portfolio for COMP500 [AUT]
item.description: COMP500: Programming Concepts and Techniques Portfolio PDF - A level Below is the combined Part A and Part B portfolios for the COMP500 paper. If the preview does not work, click the link here. From the assignment brief “The purpose of the Portfolio is for you to electronically record your personal COMP500/ENSE501- related learning activities throughout the semester as evidence of sustained learning. Each student’s Portfolio will be creative, unique, and personal – there is no prescribed, pre-made template to follow.
